{
  "1781890": {
    "name": "昏迷 2B：地下墓穴",
    "steam_appid": 1781890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/c49fd1c4dead15980e11444548aff2f4.avif?t=1742822187\" width=622 height=205 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英豪终于逃离了名为「昏迷」的可怕镜像世界，回到了学校，过着惬意的日子。但是……怪事发生了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/9230363aa64a85f15a53a2b4e83f512a.webp?t=1742822187\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英豪的第二次冒险开始了。「昏迷」世界凶险异常，虽然逃出恐怖镜像维度的可能性微乎其微，但英豪还是抱着一丝希望，收集艺瑟的笔记，试图找到可以对付恶毒姐妹的强大宝剑。然而，某个不速之客也突然来到「昏迷」世界，局面开始变得愈加复杂。一名与艺瑟息息相关的全新角色也前来帮助英豪。在妖怪市场下方的巨大设施，英豪能否解开背后的谜团，击败恶毒姐妹？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/ef8a090dfc9fc5d03aabfa1f5d922cdb.poster.avif?t=1742822187\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/ef8a090dfc9fc5d03aabfa1f5d922cdb.webm?t=1742822187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/ef8a090dfc9fc5d03aabfa1f5d922cdb.mp4?t=1742822187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/2a944babbd8f6411f5d9373dcf7b6b92.webp?t=1742822187\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《昏迷2B：地下墓穴》是一款韩系生存恐怖冒险游戏。作为《昏迷2：恶毒姐妹》的前作，你将体验与全系列一脉相承的剧情，扮演《昏迷1》中的主角英豪，再次闯入可怕的镜像世界。《昏迷1》和《昏迷2》之间究竟发生过什么故事？在本作中找出答案吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在氛围诡异的世华区，邂逅有趣角色，解决谜题，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到线索，在狂人追杀下求得生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >奔跑或舞动手电筒会让你更容易受到攻击。生存固然重要，但探索也刻不容缓——你必须二者兼顾！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/0cdbfc31f6c2bcad2bf9758c0f29bf93.poster.avif?t=1742822187\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/0cdbfc31f6c2bcad2bf9758c0f29bf93.webm?t=1742822187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/0cdbfc31f6c2bcad2bf9758c0f29bf93.mp4?t=1742822187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/9e0ba4755e96d5ed28834ce17fc82fa1.webp?t=1742822187\" width=610 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅要面对被无情追杀的恐惧，还有凶残程度更高一级的AI！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在妖怪市场交易物品，为生死关头做好准备</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索噩梦般的世华区，揭开当地的黑暗秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜刮资源，熬过险象环生的遭遇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁工具，不断升级，造访以前无法进入的区域</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找地方躲避敌人追踪，逃出死局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生动的手绘视觉效果和连环漫画</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/84d78e8e01c7b3028b36e912e93f759d.poster.avif?t=1742822187\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/84d78e8e01c7b3028b36e912e93f759d.webm?t=1742822187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781890/extras/84d78e8e01c7b3028b36e912e93f759d.mp4?t=1742822187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
